Text: The earnings component of an annuity withdrawal is taxed as ordinary income and, if taken before age 59½, may be subject to a 10% federal income tax penalty.
Cause: The earnings component of an annuity withdrawal is taxed as ordinary income and, if taken before age 59½
Effect: may be subject to a 10% federal income tax penalty.
